dct_description_sm: from a trigonometrical survey under the direction of A.D. Bache, superintendent of the Survey of the Coast of the United States ; triangulation by E. Blunt and A.M. Harrison ; topography by A.M. Harrison ; hydrography by the party under the command of F.P. Webber.
Depths shown by soundings and contours.
"The triangulation was executed in 1843 & '63. The topography d[itt]o in 1864. The hydrography d[itt]o in 1865 and '66".
Includes information on tides and soundings.
dct_publisher_sm: Survey of the the Coast of the United States]
